Debugging Programs

pdb is a built in python module which we can use to debug a program while it is running.

---> running pdb as a script

python3 -m pdb file_name.py

Some debugging tools

- Pyflakes
- Pylint
- PyChecker
- Pep8

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Logging

Logging Levels Are --->

- CRITICAL
- ERROR
- WARNING
- INFO
- DEBUG

